File: Eskom says it's investigating the cause of the unit trips. JOHANNESBURG - Eskom has warned that there is a likelihood of load-shedding on Saturday night. READ: Eskom gets tough on municipal debt The power utility says this is because of multiple generation unit trips. Although Eskom managed to avoid outages for the last two weeks, it also warns load-shedding might be implemented throughout the weekend. Eskom says it's investigating the cause of the unit trips.